item.dc:creator: @ztr_zac1 ztr zac
item.description:
@ztr_zac1 wrote:

The add model command is a client side command, and when used the client looks in a certain directory within the client hierarchy for the model you want to add. Make sure the number corresponds with the model file name, and also ensure that it is in the correct directory.
